Cell["\<\
Velocity - angular integration:
I.36 of Del Nobile sets up angular integration: H= v f(v) from dRT/dET \
integral\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.911408973146742*^9, 3.911408987659102*^9}, {
